Ice::

Smiling. "Good, then I can learn from you both. Let's go outside. 
There isn't room in here." She walked out of the room. The clipoeard 
and pen floated beind her. She walked to the entrance and opened the 
doors. She stepped out and inhaled the crisp, clean winter 
air. "Ahhh, it's wonderful to be outside again." She took a few steps 
away from the base.  She went and stoos about 10 yards out and waited.
